{"tid":1744993,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"轉寄：早上十點後關票站","createTime":"2019-11-22T04:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T05:44:12.000Z","uid":193328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6c151f103f6a5dc1d063cf894d9cd96194b1621f","tid":1744993,"uid":193328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:15:23.000Z","msg":"轉寄：<br />\n只要票站開左3個鐘都會計算在內。<br />\n<br />\n馮驊說，只要有票站持續三小時有混亂，即停止選舉。即只要早上十點後關票站，都會計算在內。<br />\n<br />\n怪不得有建制派攪飲早茶團，今次調轉來，係朝早7點投完票先一齊去飲茶。<br />\n<br />\n呢招果然絕呀！<br />\n<br />\n同埋只要建制早上一夠票，即刻派人扮黑衣人在選舉站前搗亂，然後大有藉口把選舉煞停，咁就 sure win....."},{"pid":"0d453d89a15509c9a7169026356860df12364d27","tid":1744993,"uid":167289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:23:32.000Z","msg":"Source?"},{"pid":"b96dc1dec1633ee1cda3cb35c93086f306406c7d","tid":1744993,"uid":106800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:37:53.000Z","msg":"就係冇source <br />\n好怪<br />\n真係想我地早投再换票箱？"},{"pid":"4a7091290c959c4544ea05817b1a6826c8cea248","tid":1744993,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:40:20.000Z","msg":"我估呢堆wts一定不是建制派出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(全部人入)整合左投票前後注意事項，教埋你點樣拆種票<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezwtrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezwtrS</a>"},{"pid":"e5cf2ffeca290dbf43d9daaefd66b63c282819ea","tid":1744993,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:44:12.000Z","msg":"當啲長輩grp都開始轉發嘅時候 我就知道係流料"}]}